---
// Footer component - following Practical UI patterns
// Links in navigation context don't need underlines
---

<footer class="border-t border-light bg-lightest py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-4 no-underline">
          <img
            src="/logo.png"
            alt="PrimeBridge Finance"
            class="h-10 w-auto"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="text-dark text-base max-w-md">
          The private credit infrastructure layer. We standardize the pipe, not the product.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation Links (no underlines needed per Practical UI) -->
      <nav aria-label="Platform links">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-darkest mb-4">Platform</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/platform" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">Why PrimeBridge</a></li>
          <li><a href="/lender/register" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">List loan pools</a></li>
          <li><a href="/investor/register" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">Investor access</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <nav aria-label="Company links">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-darkest mb-4">Company</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">Privacy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms" class="text-dark hover:text-darkest no-underline">Terms</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-light">
      <p class="text-sm text-dark leading-relaxed">
        PrimeBridge Finance is a technology platform, not a bank. Loans are issued by partner financial institutions and/or special purpose entities. Investing in private credit involves risk, including loss of principal. This site is for informational purposes only and does not constitute an offer or solicitation of securities.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-dark mt-4">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} PrimeBridge Finance. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
